'''Prostitot''' is a derogatory [[United States|American]] term for [[prepubescent]] girls who dress to emulate the dress styles and attitudes of [[twenty something]] women such as [[Britney Spears]]. It especially means those who wear tight jeans and bare belly shirts.Also included are form fitting short shirts, [[miniskirt]]s and heavy makeup. The age category is generally considered to be 10 to 14 year olds. 


History: origionally this word was coined by the following people:Jason Hutzler, Brian Roskovich, and John Harbick. After a wave of britany spears fans overran their home town and they needed something new to refer to them as.  Though it was origionally a joke when first stated it flowed easily over the lips and soon was a regular part of their vocabulary.  As with most words this resulted in its slow spread and after being placed as a description for several youths in chatrooms soon it spread like wild fire and the origional creators were soon forgotten.


